453
00:22:21,000 --> 00:22:22,050
Have you made contact?

454
00:22:22,050 --> 00:22:22,860
Yes, we have.

455
00:22:23,080 --> 00:22:24,310
A shareholder from Luobai said

456
00:22:24,310 --> 00:22:25,590
the last time he saw Luo Haoran

