529
00:24:47,230 --> 00:24:48,770
The watch, the watch!

530
00:24:48,800 --> 00:24:50,750
It's worth hundreds of thousands yuan now. I'll give it to you.

531
00:24:50,750 --> 00:24:51,780
I'll give it to you.

