00:28:57,220 --> 00:28:59,620
Yeah, he has had asthma since he was little.

600
00:28:59,660 --> 00:29:00,670
Pack this up.

601
00:29:01,480 --> 00:29:03,540
Are you still worried about your dad?

602
00:29:04,400 --> 00:29:06,000
